# Workflow layer (Service)

## Read first

- `internal/workflow/booking/workflow.go` — state machine, timer, updates
- `internal/workflow/booking/payment.go` — validation simulation
- `internal/workflow/booking/activities.go` — repository side effects
- [docs/design_overview.md](../../docs/design_overview.md) §3

## Boundaries

- No Gin/HTTP imports in this package.
- One `BookingWorkflow` per order; workflow ID equals `order_id`.
- Seat mutations only via activities → `SeatRepository` (`TryHold`, `Release`, `Confirm`, `SwapHold`).
- Payment uses workflow **updates** (`UpdateSubmitPayment`), not signal polling.
- Timer starts on **first seat hold** (`PATCH /seats` with non-empty seats); **refreshes** on every seat change (S-2); **never pauses** during payment (S-4). No timer in `CREATED` state.
- Enforce 3 consecutive failed payment attempts → `PAYMENT_FAILED` (S-3). No per-code / per-method distinction.

